Tax Ombud Bernard Ngoepe just visited the offices of Polokwane Observer to discuss the services provided by the Office of the Tax Ombud (OTO).
In his message Ngoepe invited members of the public to take advantage of the opportunity to meet with officials of the OTO who are available at the Game foyer at Mall of the North as well as outside Mugg & Bean in Savannah Mall from today until Sunday to inform the public.
Story and photo: BARRY VILJOEN
>>barryv.observer@gmail.com

Tax Ombud Bernard Ngoepe and Senior Communications Manager of the OTO, Pearl Seopela.